{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"97ff89d91a","title":"中央统战部关于“民主人士”的定义问题：复西北局统战部","origin":"中共中央统一战线工作部编《统战政策文件汇编》（1-4册 共4册），1958年。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c94065e88c","index":0,"year":1951,"month":6,"day":16,"articleId":"97ff89d91a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"17e1d4270f","type":"title","text":"中央统战部关于“民主人士”的定义问题：复西北局统战部","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"97ff89d91a"},{"id":"7d532003ad","type":"paragraph","text":"你们四月十日来电所询关于“民主人士”的定义问题，答复如下：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"97ff89d91a"},{"id":"f5f53e9c3e","type":"paragraph","text":"“民主人士”是对参加人民民主运动的某些党外人士（包括有党派和无党派）的一种政治称号，一般的说“民主人士”应具备下列两个条件：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"97ff89d91a"},{"id":"7051708149","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）解放前多少参加过人民民主运动（包括起义在内）或在解放前采取善意中立态度而在解放后参加人民民主活动。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"97ff89d91a"},{"id":"d820ceadf2","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）在中间阶层或民主党派中有一定的代表性。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"97ff89d91a"}],"page":{"id":"3d3a4a9af7","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"97ff89d91a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}